<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />In you, Yahweh, I take refuge;</para>

<para style="q1">never let me be humiliated.</para>

<para style="q1">Rescue me in your righteousness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Listen to me; rescue me quickly;</para>

<para style="q1">be my rock of refuge,</para>

<para style="q1">a stronghold to save me.</para>
